title: random branch sort
pid: 361fb584-4c17-4c1c-b6db-2153489f70ad
body: |2-
  Define something like this:
    (defun my-org-random-sort ()
      (random 1000))
  Highlight the branches to sort.
  Then run:
    C-c ^ f               ;; C-c ^ = org-sort
    my-org-random-sort
    RET
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
